      "weather": "FINE",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BINNAWAY WIZARD (2) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 0.8 lengths win at Murray Bridge in a handy 22.59. Fair draw can see a good run and has a good record over this journey. Expected to be right there at the finish again. ZINFANDEL DASH (5) has some solid form under her belt and proved too classy last time to win by one length at Gawler in a handy 22.82 beating Hijinkery. Shapes as a top winning chance on latest effort. ZING MATILDA (1) broke a string of placings finishing in the money four on end before a last start fifth (20.47) at this track. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to her name from six starts. Expected to feature in the finish. RINGO ROSE (8) deserves plenty of thought at his first run at this distance.",
